    {
      "version": "8.0.0",
      "date": "February 16, 2022",
      "changelog": [
        {
          "type": "breaking_changes",
          "changes": [
            "Segmented controls are now in three sizes: <br />Small -> Medium <br />Medium -> Large <br />New Small size (smaller than the previous) <br /><strong>How to fix</strong>: Check where you are using segmented controls and update the sizes to the correct new size. If you have no specified size add <span class=\"code-text\">e-segmented-controls--lg</span> and if you have the small size specified (<span class=\"code-text\">e-segmented-controls--sm</span>) just remove the specification to receive medium size instead.",
            "Title xs on mobiles has been updated font-size from 18px -> 16px. This is done so that the difference between title sm and xs i more distinct.<strong>How to fix</strong>: You should not have to change anything here, just be aware that title-xs is smaller.",
            "Toggle has updated structure and now includes label and role. This is done for better accessibility.<strong>How to fix</strong>: Replace the old structure for all your toggles with the structure in the <a class=\"e-link e-link--inline\" href=\"https://design.elvia.io/components/toggle#Overview\">examples</a>."
          ],
          "components": [
            {
              "displayName": "Segmented Control",
              "url": "https://design.elvia.io/components/segmented-control#Size"
            },
            { "displayName": "Toggle", "url": "https://design.elvia.io/components/toggle" }
          ],
          "pages": [{ "displayName": "Typography", "url": "https://design.elvia.io/brand/typography" }]
        }
