            "The design and structure of tables have been updated. Tables with black headers have been removed and a wrapper class has been added.How to fix:Add an element with the <span class=\"code-text changelog-code\">e-table-container</span> class outside the element with the <span class=\"code-text changelog-code\">e-table</span> class.<span class=\"code-text changelog-code\">e-table</span> -> <span class=\"code-text changelog-code\">e-table-container e-table</span>"
